Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:52.31,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抜け出して　自由になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:58.84,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:06.15,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.34,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:16.91,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:23.24,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever

Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.68,0:25:26.41,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘をついた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.03,0:25:32.68,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに　怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.70,0:25:39.16,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧哗をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.05,0:25:46.52,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は　忘れていた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:53.57,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が　青いこと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.34,0:26:00.68,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが　嬉しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.83,0:26:07.09,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:14.15,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.94,0:26:20.30,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.44,0:26:25.80,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃

Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.75,0:26:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\pos(512,550)\1c&H00d9ebea}预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.03,0:26:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁输了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.03,0:26:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“艾里克斯”怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.00,0:27:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克其小姐，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.03,0:27:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁最坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.03,0:27:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，你赢得了那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.35,0:27:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\pos(512,520)\1c&H00d9ebea}第4话\N\N\N\N\N\N渡过河流 穿越树林


